'''科科利兹利流行病'''（英文：Cocoliztli epidemics），或'''科科利兹特利流行病'''，是对16世纪发生在[[南美洲|南美洲]][[新西班牙總督轄區|新西班牙殖民地]]（今[[墨西哥|墨西哥]]地区）[[流行病|流行病疫情]]的总称。<ref name=":1">{{Cite journal|title=Megadrought and Megadeath in 16th Century Mexico|url=https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pmc/articles/PMC2730237/|last=Acuna-Soto|first=Rodolfo|last2=Stahle|first2=David W.|date=2002-4|journal=Emerging Infectious Diseases|issue=4|doi=10.3201/eid0804.010175|volume=8|pages=360–362|issn=1080-6040|pmc=2730237|pmid=11971767|last3=Cleaveland|first3=Malcolm K.|last4=Therrell|first4=Matthew D.|access-date=2020-12-15|archive-date=2021-02-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210217203244/https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pmc/articles/PMC2730237/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name=":3">{{Cite journal|title=When half of the population died: the epidemic of hemorrhagic fevers of 1576 in Mexico|author=Rodofo Acuna-Soto, David W. Stahle, Matthew D. Therrell, Richard D. Griffin, Malcolm K. Cleaveland|url=https://academic.oup.com/femsle/article/240/1/1/536409|journal=FEMS Microbiology Letter|issue=1|doi=|others=|year=2004|volume=240|page=|pmid=|access-date=2020-12-15|archive-date=2021-02-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210208000557/https://academic.oup.com/femsle/article/240/1/1/536409|dead-url=no}}</ref> 疫情的病因不明，可能包含有多种[[流行病|流行病]]，主要症状包括[[高燒|高烧]]和耳鼻流血，当地的[[阿兹特克人|阿兹特克人]]将此病称为“科科利兹特利（Cocoliztli）”，意味“[[瘟疫|瘟疫]]”（[[納瓦特爾語|纳瓦特尔语]]）。<ref name=":1" /><ref name=":3" /><ref name=":0">{{Cite web|title=法媒：科学家发现阿兹特克文明或毁于“肠热病”|url=http://news.sina.com.cn/o/2018-01-17/doc-ifyqtycw8935873.shtml|accessdate=2020-12-15|author=|date=2018-01-17|last=|format=|work=|publisher=参考消息|agency=新浪|language=}}</ref><ref name=":2">{{Cite web|title=One of history's worst epidemics may have been caused by a common microbe|url=https://www.sciencemag.org/news/2018/01/one-history-s-worst-epidemics-may-have-been-caused-common-microbe|accessdate=2020-12-15|author=Angus Chen|date=2018-01-16|last=|first=|format=|work=|publisher=《[[科学_(期刊)|科学]]》（''Science''）|language=en|archive-date=2021-01-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210119003029/https://www.sciencemag.org/news/2018/01/one-history-s-worst-epidemics-may-have-been-caused-common-microbe|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name=":4">{{Cite web|title=史上最嚴重的 20 次流行病——從史前到現代|url=https://www.chainnews.com/zh-hant/articles/554428651278.htm|accessdate=2020-12-15|work=ChainNews|language=zh-hant}}</ref>

此次疫情分为两拨，共造成了700万 - 1750万人死亡，是历史上[[流行病列表|致死人数最多的流行病之一]]，也是墨西哥历史上最严重的流行病疫情。<ref name=":1" /><ref name=":3" /><ref name=":0" /> 第一波疫情爆发于1545年-1548年间，造成死亡500万-1500万人（约80%的墨西哥人口）；第二波疫情爆发于1576年-1578年间，造成死亡200万-250万人（约50%的墨西哥人口）。<ref name=":1" /><ref name=":3" />

有历史学家认为，该流行病可能是[[天花|天花]]、[[斑疹傷寒|斑疹伤寒]]或[[麻疹|麻疹]]，但实际症状并不一致。<ref>{{Cite web|title=La epidemia de cocoliztli de 1576|url=https://www.estudioshistoricos.inah.gob.mx/revistaHistorias/wp-content/uploads/historias_11_24-33.pdf|accessdate=|author=Eisa Malvido, Carlos Viesca|date=|format=|publisher=|language=|archive-date=2021-01-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210129003100/https://www.estudioshistoricos.inah.gob.mx/revistaHistorias/wp-content/uploads/historias_11_24-33.pdf|dead-url=no}}</ref> 也有人认为是[[病毒性出血熱|病毒性出血热]]，而当时严重的旱情加重了疫情。<ref name=":1" /><ref name=":2" /> 当代科学研究认为，[[沙門氏菌感染症|沙门氏菌感染症]]至少是科科利兹利流行病中的一种，由当时的欧洲[[殖民者|殖民者]]带入。<ref name=":0" /><ref name=":2" /><ref name=":4" /><ref>{{Cite journal|title=Salmonella enterica genomes recovered from victims of a major 16th century epidemic in Mexico|url=https://www.biorxiv.org/content/10.1101/106740v2|last=Vågene|first=Åshild J.|last2=Campana|first2=Michael G.|date=2017-02-08|journal=bioRxiv|doi=10.1101/106740|pages=106740|language=en|last3=García|first3=Nelly M. Robles|last4=Warinner|first4=Christina|last5=Spyrou|first5=Maria A.|last6=Valtueña|first6=Aida Andrades|last7=Huson|first7=Daniel|last8=Tuross|first8=Noreen|last9=Herbig|first9=Alexander|access-date=2020-12-15|archive-date=2021-02-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210212015500/https://www.biorxiv.org/content/10.1101/106740v2|dead-url=no}}</ref>

